{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/qMYb0pTEnsYsYPVD1uJIpOMumYB.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Drama"},{"id":35,"name":"Comedy"}],"homepage":"","id":1107215,"imdb_id":"tt29927144","origin_country":["FR"],"original_language":"fr","original_title":"Ma mère, Dieu et Sylvie Vartan","overview":"In 1963, Esther gives birth to Roland, the youngest of a large family. Roland is born with a club foot that prevents him from standing. Against everyone's advice, she promises her son that he will walk like the others and that he will have a fabulous life. From then on, Esther will do everything in her power to keep this promise. Through decades of trials and miracles of life, this film is the story of a true, funny and moving story, that of an incredible destiny and the greatest love there is: that of a mother for her child.","popularity":1.0175,"poster_path":"/9MZjFDA3ILz3n23Iqj1ozYfi8yt.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":95493,"logo_path":null,"name":"Egérie Productions","origin_country":"FR"},{"id":9,"logo_path":"/nda3dTUYdDrJ6rZqBpYvY865aDv.png","name":"Gaumont","origin_country":"FR"},{"id":749,"logo_path":"/vdl6tOwJ4O75gFEC5gDk17Fop88.png","name":"Christal Films","origin_country":"CA"},{"id":210099,"logo_path":"/g5oRCNCi8kNVb8gEoSoIcqkhjmR.png","name":"Amazon MGM Studios","origin_country":"US"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","name":"France"},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","name":"Canada"},{"iso_3166_1":"US","name":"United States of America"}],"release_date":"2025-03-19","revenue":12377729,"runtime":102,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"French","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Once Upon My Mother","video":false,"vote_average":6.965,"vote_count":244,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","title":"Once Upon My Mother","type":""},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","title":"Моя мама волшебница","type":""},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","title":"Historia de una madre","type":""}]}}